name: PIP
description: Pip the pig, born from Davedo's imagination, now encapsulating true silliness and fun on chain. Pip art is being created daily, with art presented on livestream. Pip style is rough and meme-centric, with focus on connecting with experiences, people and places. Pip launched on 4 October, marking its inception and mark into the meme-culture. The community has come together to support Pip in culture and community.
